_sText:
zm_oddbuildings is a small zombie survival map for online servers, it features lots of spots to hide and build barricades with props, to crawl into or to climb away from the reach of the zombie claws of death. It have lights, 64 player spawns, and breakable vents, barriers, and windows.
Please contact me or comment if you have any problem with the map or want me to make changes in it to better suit your server.

Version 3, better optimisation, small visual details improved and added invisible boxes to improve walking over two static props in important spots.
